        <tr><td><strong>Fallback content</strong></td><td>Resource consumers</td><td>Skeleton, empty, or stale-previous on exhaustion</td><td colspan="2">🔗 <a href="/intents/reliability/">Reliability Intent</a> fallback dimension</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Error boundary</strong></td><td>Component trees</td><td>Structural error containment above the failed subtree</td><td colspan="2">🔗 Router error boundary</td></tr>
